applicationModel.name: example-map
applicationModel.description: This application shows a map with 6 items on it, as defined in the default value. The items are localized with latitude and longitude coordinates, and are drawn as small green dots with SVG. Each item has a tooltip that opens on hover, and a dialog that opens when the item is clicked. The dialog contains an input that allows the user to edit the data available in the model of the corresponding item.
